name: The Bull Fighters Daughter, 2019
description:
Bull Fighters Daughter was a 16 x 20” MM collage on canvas. 
The original art was purchased at Imogen Gallery, Astoria, OR
https://imogengallery.com/painters-print-makers/anne-grgich

AMG website: www.annegrgich.com

Sound design by @fendelmarc
Instruments: Spitfire LABS, Elektron Model Samples, recorders, flute, keyboards, samples
Vocal samples: Reyna Zack
Recorded and mixed in Seattle, Washington - August 2021


Anne Grgich is one of the most original and innovative artists in 
the group of American artists known as Outsiders. 
Completely self-taught and in Raw Vision Magazine Woman 
Issue #103 by Colin Rhodes.
